    <p class="description">AISEO is one of the cheapest AI content tools on the market — $15/mo annual — with a heavy bet on GEO (Generative Engine Optimization) and a humanizer that <strong>only beats some AI detectors</strong>. After 14 days of testing the humanizer against 6 detectors, here is the honest 2026 verdict.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
