            <span class="cta-meta">24-hour delivery · No card</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="vs-stacc">theStacc vs AISEO — honest comparison</h2>
        <p>We wrote this review. We compete. Read the comparison first so you can weigh everything that follows.</p>

        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>AISEO</th><th>theStacc</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Starting price</td><td class="cell-yes">$15/mo (annual)</td><td>$99/mo</td></tr>
              <tr><td>AI content drafting</td><td class="cell-yes">Yes</td><td class="cell-yes">Yes — fully managed</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Humanizer (beats AI detectors)</td><td>Partial (50–75% pass rate)</td><td class="cell-yes">Editorially reviewed by humans</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Keyword research database</td><td class="cell-no">No</td><td class="cell-yes">Built-in</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Rank tracking</td><td class="cell-no">No</td><td class="cell-yes">Daily</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Auto-publishes to CMS</td><td class="cell-no">Manual export only</td><td class="cell-yes">WordPress · Webflow · Ghost</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Google Business Profile posts</td><td class="cell-no">No</td><td class="cell-yes">30 GBP posts / month</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Editorial review</td><td class="cell-no">DIY — you edit</td><td class="cell-yes">Included</td></tr>
