            <div class="cc-row cc-row-total"><span>What you actually spend</span><strong>$3,297 /mo</strong></div>
          </div>
          <div class="cc-vs">
            <span class="cc-vs-label">VS theStacc</span>
            <div class="cc-vs-row">
