        <div class="callout callout-warn">
          <div class="callout-label">⚠️ The execution math</div>
          <p>AISEO drafts are usable but heavy-edit. Every article needs 30–60 minutes of editor time to remove AI repetition, fact-check claims, and tighten flow. At freelance editor rates ($40–80/hr), that is $1,200–$2,400/mo on top of the subscription for 30 articles.</p>
