              <li>No CMS publishing — copy-paste only</li>
              <li>$1 trial auto-converts in 3 days, cancellation friction</li>
              <li>Output gets repetitive after 10–15 articles (same intros / hooks)</li>
              <li>GEO marketing oversells what's actually a basic FAQ block</li>
              <li>No editorial review — you fact-check and edit yourself</li>
              <li>Non-English output drops in quality outside top 4 languages</li>
              <li>No team collaboration features below Premium tier</li>
