        </div>

        <h2 id="performance">Performance — humanizer pass rates tested</h2>
        <p>The humanizer is the feature most users buy AISEO for. Here is the actual pass rate against six detectors (50 paragraphs each, GPT-4 source, June 2026 testing):</p>

        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">75%</div><div class="stat-lbl">Pass rate vs ZeroGPT</div></div>
          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">62%</div><div class="stat-lbl">Pass rate vs Originality.ai</div></div>
