        <p><strong>The detection arms race never stops.</strong> Whatever pass rate AISEO reports today, expect detector models to catch up within 60–90 days. If your publishing strategy depends entirely on bypassing detectors, you are betting against an industry with bigger budgets than your humanizer vendor.</p>

        <blockquote class="pull">
          "AISEO is fine. It's $15. I expected $15 of value and got $15 of value. The humanizer is hit-or-miss. The drafts need real edits. But for what it costs, I am not complaining."
